Content Distribution Engine (CDE)
Documentation Master Plan (Aligned to NS-GGP Canonical Template)
PurposeThis document defines the authoritative documentation master plan for CDE, strictly aligned to the existing NS-GGP document structure (000–014).
CDE is the content packaging, scheduling, and distribution engine for Northfield Solidarity. It is responsible for taking approved content artifacts and reliably distributing them across internal and external channels. CDE does notgenerate insights (PIE), govern approvals (GGP), or manage identity (IDN).

CDE Documentation Index (Canonical)

