Cross-Engine Dependencies
CDE integrates with but does not own:
GGP — content approval and governance
IDN — channel identities and credentials
MUX — external distribution adapters
SIG — content performance signals

Completion Criteria
CDE documentation is complete when:
NS-CDE-000 → NS-CDE-014 exist
Content cannot be published without approval
Distribution actions are auditable
Emergency controls are effective

